title: John H. Cox
added: After Cox lost the 2018 gubernatorial election in California, it was widely speculated that Cox might seek the office again.{{source?|date=November 2020}} In September 2020, Cox officially launched an exploratory committee for a 2022 gubernatorial run.<ref>[https://www.foxla.com/news/john-cox-launches-exploratory-committee-to-challenge-gavin-newsom-in-2022-the-state-is-in-crisis Fox 11 Los Angeles - "John Cox launches exploratory committee to challenge Gavin Newsom in 2022: 'The state is in crisis'"]</ref><ref>[https://californiaglobe.com/fr/john-cox-forms-exploratory-committee-for-2022-gubernatorial-run/ California Globe - "John Cox Forms Exploratory Committee For 2022 Gubernatorial Run"]</ref>
